### HOWTO : node package manager

update packages                      ncu --interactive --format group
install package (global)             npm -g install <package>
update installed package (global)    npm -g update <package>
show packages versions (local)       npm list --depth=0
show packages versions (global)      npm list -g --depth=0
show packages versions (repo)        npm show <package> version
create package-lock.json             npm i --package-lock-only

